 P2y.jp  https://p2y.jp VTuber最新消息2024 年 3 月 18 日星期一 16:44:07 +0000贾每小时1 https://wordpress.org/?v=6.4.3 https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cropped-logo_2023_150x150-32x32.png P2y.jp https://p2y.jp 32 32 166157578
 Akemi Nekomachi 是第一位订阅人数达到 200 万的男性 VTuber。 https://p2y.jp/akemi-nekomachi-became-the-first-male-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/ https://p2y.jp/akemi-nekomachi-became-the-first-male-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/#respondp2y_admin Mon, 18 Mar 2024 16:42:00 +0000 VTuberバーチャルAKA VirtualAkemi Nekomachi(猫町アケミ)YouTuberインドネシアチャンネル登録者数(YouTube)バーチャルYouTuber https://p2y.jp/?p=119252 <p>截至 2024 年 3 月 18 日（Reiwa 6），VTuber Akemi Nekomachi（Akemi Nekomachi/隶属关系：AKA Virtual）的官方 YouTube 频道有 20 名订阅者 [...]</p>猫町明美<a href="https://p2y.jp/akemi-nekomachi-became-the-first-male-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/">(Akemi Nekomachi) 成为第一位订阅人数达到 200 万的男性 VTuber 的帖子</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>截至 2024 年 3 月 18 日，VTuber <strong>Akemi Nekomachi</strong> （隶属关系：AKA Virtual）的官方 YouTube 频道已有 200 万订阅者。<strong>他成为第一位订阅人数达到 200 万的男性明星</strong>。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1200" height="674" data-attachment-id="104805" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/aka-virtual-announced-akemi-nekomachi-was-the-worlds-no-1-youtube-subscribers-male-vtuber/akemi_nekomachi_image/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/akemi_nekomachi_image.png" data-orig-size="1200,674" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="akemi_nekomachi_image" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/akemi_nekomachi_image.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/akemi_nekomachi_image.png" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/akemi_nekomachi_image.png" alt="AKA Virtual成员Akemi Nekomachi宣布成为全球订阅人数最多的男性VTuber。" class="wp-image-104805"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> Akemi Nekomachi 图片来源：新闻稿 © 2023 • AKA VIRTUAL </figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="119254" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/akemi-nekomachi-became-the-first-male-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/akemi_nekomachi_youtube_subscribers_2m/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/akemi_nekomachi_youtube_subscribers_2m.png" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Akemi Ch. 猫町アケミ【AKA Virtual】" data-image-description="&lt;p>;Akemi Ch. 猫町アケミ【AKA Virtual】&lt;/p>;
